        <div class="print-content"><article id="node-12426" class="node node-contentpage node-content-12426 clearfix" about="/content/international-agreements-ip" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" role="article">

        <h2>
      International agreements on IP
    </h2>
    <span property="dc:title" content="International agreements on IP" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><span property="sioc:num_replies" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>
  
  <div class="content clearfix">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>There are two main types of multilateral agreements concerning IP: (a) general conventions offering minimum standards and rules for protecting IP rights and (b) conventions on specific subject matter that include substantive provisions (rules that determine the rights and obligations of the parties) and/or procedural rules (which govern the process for obtaining and enforcing those rights and duties) for particular types of IP rights (e.g. patents, trademarks, utility models, etc.). These include the TRIPS, the Paris Convention and the Patent Cooperation Treaty, among others.&nbsp;</p></div>
      </div>
</div>

<div class="paragraphs-items paragraphs-items-field-paragraphs paragraphs-items-field-paragraphs-print paragraphs-items-print">
  <div class="field field-name-field-paragraphs field-type-paragraphs field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even"><div class="entity entity-paragraphs-item paragraphs-item-ipp-topic-body" about="" typeof="">
  <div class="content">
    <div class="field field-name-field-paragraph-title field-type-text field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even">Which are the main international IP agreements and their main characteristics?</div>
      </div>
</div>
<div class="field field-name-field-paragraph-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item even"><div style="text-align: justify;"><br /><strong>Table 1 gives an overview of some of the main international IP agreements.</strong></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>
<table class="MsoNormalTable" style="margin: auto auto auto 0.1pt; border: currentColor; width: 586px;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 39.55pt; mso-yfti-irow: 0; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes;">
<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; border: 1pt solid black; width: 67.65pt; height: 39.55pt; background-color: transparent; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt;" width="90">
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: center; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;" align="center"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-US;" lang="EN-GB" data-mce-mark="1">Type</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: black black black #000000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 180.45pt; height: 39.55pt; background-color: transparent; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid black .5pt;" width="241">
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: center; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;" align="center"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-US;" lang="EN-GB" data-mce-mark="1">Agreement</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: black black black #000000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 191.35pt; height: 39.55pt; background-color: transparent; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid black .5pt;" width="255">
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: center; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;" align="center"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-US;" lang="EN-GB" data-mce-mark="1">Description</span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 39.55pt; page-break-inside: avoid; mso-yfti-irow: 1;">
<td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: #000000 black black; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 67.65pt; height: 39.55pt; background-color: transparent; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid black .5pt;" rowspan="2" width="90">
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-language: EN-US;" lang="EN-GB" data-mce-mark="1">No subject-matter specific international IP agreements</span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: #000000 black black #000000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 180.45pt; height: 39.55pt; background-color: transparent; mso-border-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-left-alt: solid black .5pt; mso-border-top-alt: solid black .5pt;" width="241">
